name: Alchemy Ring Physical Item
description:
This is a voucher for a physical item created by Mountain Cut Studio in Australia. ​www.mountaincut.com.au

It is a ring made of titanium to fit US size 11.5 and has the serial number alch.21.2

This voucher may be freely traded and anyone who controls the NFT may redeem the physical item by contacting info@mountaincut.com.au and sending the NFT back to the originating account: mountaincut.tez 

mountaincut.tez will then produce a *certificate NFT* to replace the *voucher NFT* and send the physical item to the physical address given.

The voucher is valid for 1 year from first purchase, but may be renewed in 1 year blocks by contacting info@mountaincut.com.au . Shipping / insurance up to $80USD will be provided, but local taxes are the purchases responsibility.
